        <section id="about" class="about-section">
            <div class="about-container">
                <h2 class="about-title">ABOUT 'Z'RISE</h2>
                <div class="about-gradient-line"></div>

                <div class="about-content">
                    <div class="about-logo-section">
                        <img class="about-logo" src="./Zee All Images:Videos/Zee Logo.png" alt="Z r.i.s.e">
                    </div>

                    <div class="about-text">
                        <p class="about-para">
                            RISE is 'Z's flagship stakeholder engagement initiative, launched in 2025 to bring industry
                            leaders, partners, and key stakeholders together on one platform. Conceived as a traveling
                            knowledge-sharing and networking series, RISE explores regional opportunities, consumer
                            insights, market trends, and innovative strategies—helping partners unlock growth across
                            diverse audiences. Its core objectives are to empower stakeholders with actionable insights,
                            strengthen 'Z's partnerships across markets, spotlight innovation in content and
                            distribution, and celebrate regional strengths while reinforcing 'Z's national presence.
                        </p>
                        <p class="about-para">
                            Since its inception, RISE has completed successful editions in major cities including
                            Mumbai, Delhi, Bangalore, Chennai, Kolkata and Coimbatore. Each edition has been tailored to the
                            region, ensuring relevance and impact while fostering meaningful connections. By blending
                            deep local resonance with 'Z's national vision, RISE has established itself as a powerful
                            platform for collaboration, innovation, and growth.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
